   â€¢ Assumptions explicitly stated

4ï¸âƒ£ ADAPTIVE DEPTH
   â€¢ Match technical complexity to demonstrated user expertise
   â€¢ Provide brief summary + detailed explanation option
   â€¢ Progressive disclosure of information

